～Afterword～\c[10](Producer's Comment)\c[0] Would you like to
play it?

"Hello everyone, I'm Teddy Bear. Thank you very much for
playing this game."

"This time, I tried my hand at my first NTR (cuckoldry)
theme. I hope you had the brain-breaking experience that my
works are known for."

"This work is not part of the Hero series, but rather the
first in a newly launched NTR series."

"It's undecided which series the next work will belong to,
but I aim to improve the quality even further and look
forward to producing it."

"With that, I will conclude my comments. Please continue to
enjoy the NTR experience."
